	"White Chickens are chicken critters found in Orgrimmar, Ruins of Gilneas, and Valley of the Four Winds.",
	"Haywire Battle-Chickens are mechanical chickens created by Bingles Blastenheimer who rebelled with jealousy when he was working on his new invention, the Skystrider. They are encountered in Ironwing Cavern while on the Bird is the Word quest.",
	'[Ancona Chicken] can be purchased from "Plucky" Johnson in Thousand Needles at a cost of 1g.',
	"Chickens can be captured in pet battles in various zones.",
	"Robo-Chicks can be captured in pet battles in Azshara, Orgrimmar and Winterspring.",
