	"[Gnomish Battle Chicken] can be crafted by Gnome Engineers.",
	"Condors are carrion birds, found in the Redridge Mountains, Borean Tundra, and Dragonblight.",
	"Carrion Condors are found in Transborea, a region of Borean Tundra.",
