	'Dire Condors are carrion birds found in the Redridge Mountains. They drop Condor Giblets which are used for the quest "Franks and Beans".',
	"Dragonbone Condors are found in the Dragon Wastes of Dragonblight, living on the bones of the dead dragons.",
	"Fleshbeak Scavengers are condors located near Karabor in Shadowmoon Valley.",
	"Frostbeak Scavengers, Frostfire Bonestrippers, Frostfire Fleshrippers, Juvenile Bonestrippers and Trained Bonestrippers are found in Frostfire Ridge.",
