	"Thunderbirds and Trenchwing Scavengers are condors found in Krasarang Wilds.",
	"Arae is a rare condor located in the hills immediately south of Sun Rock Retreat in Stonetalon Mountains.",
	"Corpsefeeder is a rare carrion bird located near the Forsaken Front in Silverpine Forest.",
	"Dreadtalon is a condor found in the Dragon Wastes of Dragonblight. He has been attacking numerous Horde caravans traveling to and from Venomspite, and for this Captain Gort has orders from Overlord Agmar to tell players to kill him.",
	"Lord Condar is a rare condor found southwest of Farstrider Lodge in Loch Modan. He is on a 2-3 hour respawn timer.",
	'The  [Blue Mini Jouster] and  [Gold Mini Jouster] are the possible quest rewards for "Egg Wave". Both of them carry little straw puppets with toy pikes on their heads.',
	"Cranes are large birds native to Pandaria, and also found in the Shadowlands in Bastion and Ardenweald. They make their first appearance in Mists of Pandaria, and later in Shadowlands. These creatures should not be confused with tallstriders.",
	"Chi-Ji the Red Crane is one of the four creatures known as the August Celestials who watch over Pandaria.",
	"The majestic crane is a treasured friend of the pandaren.",
	"The pandaren of the Krasarang Wilds believe the cranes of Krasarang to be gifts from Chi-Ji, and their feathers are used to adorn garments and to fletch arrows.",
	"It is said that each crane flock appoints a sentry who stands guard with a stone in its beak, so that, should it fall asleep, the stone drops and it awakens.",
	"The Windfeather species of crane, found only on the Timeless Isle, are capable of producing brilliant plumage, and are highly protective of their nests.",
	"The Windfeather species of crane seem to have an affinity with the winds, and can smooth down their feathers, allowing them to rapidly strike predators.",
	"The matriarchs of the Windfeather species of cranes sing a soothing melody, calming the chicks when they are agitated. The males seem particularly fierce, and will ruffle their feathers to sweep a powerful gust of wind at attackers.",
	"The meat of the Windfeather cranes makes for a savory, if lean, meal. Their feathers seem to have the ability to lighten spirits, and may have magical properties.",
	"Crane chicks of the Timeless Isle sometimes sing a curious song that calms the nerves and soothes the soul.",
	"The feathers of the Windfeather crane are surprisingly light to the touch and will fly away with the slightest breeze.",
	"Autumn is a crane mount and animal companion of Lorewalker Cho. Unlike Summer and Mishi, Autumn is only seen in Cho's home at Dreamer's Pavilion in the Jade Forest.",
	"Chi-Ji the Red Crane is one of the four creatures known as the August Celestials who watch over Pandaria. He watches over the Valley of the Four Winds and Krasarang Wilds and is sometimes referred to as the Southern Celestial or the Spirit of Hope.",
