	"Patrannache is a rare elite crane found in Valley of the Four Winds. He remains invisible until a hunter uses a Flare to unveil him. He was the only pink crane found in World of Warcraft, until Brilliant Windfeathers appeared on the Timeless Isle.",
	"The Songbird Queen is a crane that can be found in the Scrollkeeper's Sanctum of the Temple of the Jade Serpent. The Songbird Queen most likely comes from the pandaren literature that been brought to life by Haunting Sha.",
	"Ancient Bloodcrown Cranes are cranes located in the Krasarang Wilds.",
