	"Oskiira the Vengeful is found just south of Talon Altar in Spires of Arak. Behind Oskiira lies a nest of broken eggs, around the nest lies the remains of a dread raven and three Sethekk Chosen.",
	"Raketalon is an dread raven located at the Ring of Trials in Nagrand. After his demise, Raketalon's spirit appears and is reunited with his offsprings.",
	"Yikkan Izu alongside Izu's Ravens are the final encounter at Rank 6 in the Brawler's Guild.",
