	"Dread Raven Hatchlings are dread ravens located in Skyreach.",
	"Lunarfall Chicks are dread ravens located in Lunarfall in Shadowmoon Valley.",
	"The Lunarfall Matriarch is found at Lunarfall before constructing the Alliance garrison. In her nest, look for the Lunarfall Egg, which contains 5-10x [Garrison Resources]. The egg can only be found while Lunarfall is not in the garrison phase.",
	"Lunarfall Ravens are dread ravens located in Moonflower Valley in Shadowmoon Valley.",
	"[Reins of the Raven Lord] has a chance to drop from Anzu in Sethekk Halls on Heroic difficulty.",
	"[Reins of the Dread Raven] is granted upon purchase of the Warlords of Draenor Collector's Edition.",
	"[Reins of the Corrupted Dreadwing] can be purchased from Dawn-Seeker Krisek <Order of the Awakened> in Tanaan Jungle at a cost of 150,000 Apexis Crystal upon reaching Friendly with Order of the Awakened.",
	"Dread ravens are tamable by hunters as part of the bird of prey family. The flightless, corrupted model is unique to only one tamable NPC: Blaithe, as Anzu cannot be tamed.",
	"A dread raven Spirit Healer can be found in a corner of Skettis in the Spires of Arak, surrounded by several kaliri spirits.",
	"Dread ravens use the same skeleton and animations as skyscreamers.",
	"Dread ravens were originally untamable by hunters due to their rarity and their ties to the arakkoa. They were made tamable in patch 8.3.0.",
